                           <note><locus target="#iii">Fols. iii, </locus> (before <locus target="#1">1, </locus>) and <locus target="#iv">iv, </locus> after (<locus target="#70">70</locus>)
                              are of a different kind of parchment, which is whiter and lighter,
                              probably European.
                              Both contain an impression, possibly from the manufacturer (CASTRE visible).</note>
